entries.femaleVariant: I want a foreigner, translator shard off. I don't want him to understand me, and I don't want to understand him.
No chit-chat. Can't take another one talking my head off.
Any preference when it comes to looks?
Hm, twenties, decent bod but not too built. Should smell nice. Be nice if he seemed intelligent, too, but it's not a must-have.
Mhm. Size? Any special gear? Something new, nova?
No nova. No surprises this time. He just needs to be good.
Well, I've got just the thing. I'm sure you two will have a wonderful cruise.
Better be wonderful. Sure paying enough.
